sentences: Oluwatosin Ajibade (born 19 July 1991), better known by his stage name Mr Eazi, is a Nigerian singer, songwriter, and entrepreneur.
Mr Eazi relocated to Kumasi, Ghana in 2008 and enrolled at KNUST, where he began booking artists to perform at college parties.
Mr Eazi released his debut mixtape About to Blow in July 2013.
1 – Accra To Lagos was released on 10 February 2017.
When he was 23 years old, he returned to Nigeria and opened his own e-commerce platform.
